<h2 class="bold font-l">King's Quest VI: Heir Today, Gone Tomorrow</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Alexander sees Cassima and the way to her in the magic mirror and tells his mother about it. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MagicMirror" class='trope-example-link'>Magic Mirror</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
